This service hook triggers a deployment on deployer.vc whenever a push is made.

Install Notes
-------------

  1. **Deployment Address** - URL of the deployment to be triggered whenever a commit/push occurs, normally in the format https://&lt;account&gt;.deployer.vc/#/deployment/&lt;deployment_id&gt
  2. **API Token** - An API token for your deployer.vc account, which can be created under https://&lt;account&gt;.deployer.vc/#/account